To get to the city you can drive on one of the new roads of Mr. Pe<0xC3><0xB1>a Nieto, which is a huge improvement compared to the cracked and bumpy roads that were rehabilitated.
Plaques with his name can also be seen at the entrance to a modern sports complex and an impressive interactive museum on climate change.
